vien.net/Vi-Trang/author-sRwDvUqTTXJgu1Qk5ewg6w">Vi Trang</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-Th%C3%A1nh-T%C3%B4ng/Qu%C3%A1-Ph%C3%B9-Tang-%C4%91%E1%BB%99/poem-wo2tKRj6sS8YOVJWCmGAwQ">Quá Phù Tang độ - 過扶桑渡</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-Th%C3%A1nh-T%C3%B4ng/author-FSJg5-ivZkPUR1nhJkA6Fg">Lê Thánh Tông</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khanh-Li%C3%AAn/T%E1%BB%91-thi-k%E1%BB%B3-02/poem-UIPEm5z1plfNQYsscvjgog">Tố thi kỳ 02 - 做詩其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khanh-Li%C3%AAn/author-6jTg5S-Pv098frpyWJuzqA">Khanh Liên</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/M%E1%BA%A1nh-Giao/Tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-An-t%E1%BA%A3o-xu%C3%A2n/poem-UYeS7NGqFE_7ceNmH4moKQ">Trường An tảo xuân - 長安早春</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/M%E1%BA%A1nh-Giao/author-lb0C1LYxo0fcanV11dmAog">Mạnh Giao</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
